flex2.compiler.common

Interface SinglePathResolver

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    VirtualFile
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConfigurationPathResolver, LocalFile, LocalFilePathResolver, NetworkFile, PathResolver, SourcePath, URLPathResolver, VirtualLocalFile

    public interface SinglePathResolver
    Defines the API for path resolver implemenations. Other than PathResolver, implemenations of this interface resolve paths in a single way.
    Author:
    Brian Deitte

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      VirtualFile resolve(String path)
      If path can be resolved, an instance of VirtualFile is returned.
